room_title: Escape room "Locked! at the Bistro!" by Unlocked! Escape Rooms in Andover
review: We did the Bistro room and had an awesome time. Our group of 8 all were able to contribute to the experience and we left beyond excited. It was great having a challenging and worthy escape room experience so close to home. Thank you Carl for a great experience. Highly recommend for a night out.
